text: Edmond Lee Browning (March 11, 1929 - July 11, 2016) was an American bishop. He was the 24th Presiding Bishop and Primate of the Episcopal Church in the United States of America from 1985 through 1997. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Presiding Bishops of the Episcopal Church in the United States of America Category:People from Corpus Christi, Texas
